  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/7b13c927535199b97f685923f60622de.poster.avif?t=1740600960\" width=480 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/7b13c927535199b97f685923f60622de.webm?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/7b13c927535199b97f685923f60622de.mp4?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>ZZZZZAAAAAAPPPPPPP!!!!!!</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've found a retro style, 2D top-down action/adventure game in the vein of select retro-gaming archetypes!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed as a Couch style local co-op or solo campaign. NOTE: Two (2) controllers are required to play a local multiplayer game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons & Power-ups</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chose to upgrade your Systems with either Shields or faster engine AND range of fire!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your Weapon at the Helipad and Seek the Upgrades in the Mesosphere!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Overcome your enemies with tact and powerful weapons!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minions & Bosses</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/dbdd31e591e23ed085dac6f09fc654a2.poster.avif?t=1740600960\" width=524 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/dbdd31e591e23ed085dac6f09fc654a2.webm?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/dbdd31e591e23ed085dac6f09fc654a2.mp4?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your abilities against a wide selection of GROUND and AIR sworn enemies and engage in epic boss fights!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is the game too easy? Try HARD MODE!!!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/7b13c927535199b97f685923f60622de.poster.avif?t=1740600960\" width=480 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/7b13c927535199b97f685923f60622de.webm?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/7b13c927535199b97f685923f60622de.mp4?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>ZZZZZAAAAAAPPPPPPP!!!!!!</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've found a retro style, 2D top-down action/adventure game in the vein of select retro-gaming archetypes!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed as a Couch style local co-op or solo campaign. NOTE: Two (2) controllers are required to play a local multiplayer game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons & Power-ups</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chose to upgrade your Systems with either Shields or faster engine AND range of fire!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your Weapon at the Helipad and Seek the Upgrades in the Mesosphere!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Overcome your enemies with tact and powerful weapons!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minions & Bosses</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/dbdd31e591e23ed085dac6f09fc654a2.poster.avif?t=1740600960\" width=524 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/dbdd31e591e23ed085dac6f09fc654a2.webm?t=1740600960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455720/extras/dbdd31e591e23ed085dac6f0